caption: A brightly colored sea slug, showcasing a vibrant pattern of blue, yellow, orange, and white stripes, stands out against the muted backdrop of a coral reef. The surrounding coral, though blurred, hints at the bustling life of the reef ecosystem, with glimpses of deeper, teal-colored waters in the distance.  The slug, likely in search of its sponge prey, adds a splash of vibrant life to this underwater scene.
technicalities: Color image, likely an underwater photograph. The image is quite blurry, particularly the fish, making details difficult to discern. The colors are somewhat muted due to the lack of sharpness.
